            <div class="aboutus-text">
                <h2>Welcome to TheCar&Bike!</h2>
                <p>we are passionate about all things on wheels. Whether you're a seasoned motor enthusiast or just starting your journey into the world of bikes and cars, we've got you covered. Our mission is to provide comprehensive, reliable, and up-to-date information on a wide range of bikes and cars to help you make informed decisions.</p>
